Package API.Update

Contains programs which downloads and installs latest version of the release builds. This package downloads the lastest builds from the servers and downloads it to the machine.
The builds have separate download channels/servers for Unix and Windows builds as specified below:

Unified Build

This is the repository of the builds hosted right on GitHub.
